    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are appropriately scoped per the MRL 2 requirements table in ASME V&V 40-2018. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 20% of experimental values across all 5 operating points. Model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device regulatory submission.",
